    public class TableBody
extends CustomPanel
    A TableWidget is a CustomPanel that represents the body of a table ( <tbody> element). You can add TableRow widgets to it, that typically contain TableCellAtomic or TableCellComposite widgets.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
